# Cards

## Color Token Reference

```ts
OVERVIEW_CARD_COLORS = { payments: "#F5FBFE", settlement: "#F0FDF4", refunds: "#FEF2F2" }
PAYMENT_SUMMARY_COLORS = { collections: "#F3F8FE", adjustments: "#FEF7F7", deductions: "#FEF7F7", settlementProcessed: "rgba(39,174,95,0.06)", availableForSettlement: "#EFF8FD" }
ACTION_CARD_COLORS = { P0: "#ffebef" (60% default → 100% hover), P1: "#fff8e1" (same) }
NOTIFICATION_CARD_COLORS = { read: "#fafafa", unread: "#F5F9FE" }
```

Radius & padding constants:
- Overview: `rounded-[20px]`, `p-5`
- Summary: `rounded-[12px]`, `p-5`
- Action/default: `rounded-[16px]`, `p-4`

---

## 1. Dashboard Metric Cards (Business Overview)

- Payments: `bg-[#F5FBFE]`, Settlement: `bg-[#F0FDF4]`, Refunds: `bg-[#FEF2F2]`
- Shape: `rounded-[20px]`, padding: `p-5`
- Layout: `flex flex-col gap-3`
- Grid: `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6`
- Top row: `flex items-start justify-between` — label + amount left, illustration right
- Label: `text-[14px] text-muted-foreground` (semantic token)
- Amount: `text-[32px] font-semibold text-foreground` (semantic token)
- Illustration: in white tile `bg-[var(--background,#ffffff)] rounded-[var(--radius-200,16px)]`
- Arrow: `ArrowRight` `size-5` — optional navigation affordance (guidelines preview)
- Divider: `border-t border-border pt-3` (semantic token)
- Footer stats: two-column layout, `text-[14px]` values / `text-[12px]` labels
- Payments success rate accent: `#00c853` in dashboard code — guidelines preview may use `#21c179`
- Hover: none on metric cards themselves (dashboard uses motion on the card shell in code)
- No CTAs inside cards

---

## 2. Action Priority Cards (Actions & Notifications Widget)

- P0 (High Priority): `bg-[#ffebef]/60`, hover: `hover:bg-[#ffebef]`
- P1 (Low Priority): `bg-[#fff8e1]/60`, hover: `hover:bg-[#fff8e1]`
- No border/stroke, `rounded-[16px]`, `p-4`, `transition-colors`
- Layout: row `flex gap-3`
- Icon: Lucide `size-5` on right side
  - P0: `text-destructive` (resolves to error red), icons like `AlertCircle`, `CreditCard`
  - P1: `text-chart-3` (resolves to warning), icons like `Shield`, `Smartphone`
- Typography:
  - Title: `text-[14px] font-semibold`
  - Body: `text-[12px]`, bold inline amounts
  - CTA link: `text-[12px] text-[#004299] hover:underline`

---

## 3. Notification Cards (Actions & Notifications Widget)

- Read: `bg-[#fafafa]`
- Unread: `bg-[#F5F9FE]` — **note:** CSS class ordering matters; unread bg must come last to win specificity
- Unread indicator: `bg-primary size-2 rounded-full` blue dot
- Shape: `rounded-[16px]`, padding: `p-[16px]`
- Hover: `hover:bg-accent/50`, `cursor-pointer`
- Typography:
  - Title: `text-[14px] font-semibold`
  - Body: `text-xs` (12px)
  - Timestamp: `text-[10px] text-muted-foreground`

---

## 4. Payment Summary Cards (Payments Page)

### Layout
- Strip: `flex items-center gap-1`
- Each card: `flex-1 rounded-[12px] p-5 flex flex-col`

### Card Colors

| Type | Background |
|---|---|
| Collections | `bg-[#F3F8FE]` |
| Adjustments | `bg-[#FEF7F7]` |
| Deductions | `bg-[#FEF7F7]` (same surface as Adjustments — solid, not tinted alpha) |
| Settlement Processed | `bg-[rgba(39,174,95,0.06)]` |
| Available for Settlement | `bg-[#EFF8FD]` |

### Card Content
- Label: `text-[14px] text-[#7e7e7e]`
- Amount: `text-[20px] font-semibold text-[#101010]`
- Divider above link: `mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-[#e0e0e0]`
- Link variants:
  - "View Breakdown": `text-[12px] text-[#004299] font-medium hover:underline` + `ChevronDown` `size-4`
  - "View Details": `text-[12px] text-[#004299] font-medium hover:underline` + `ChevronRight` `size-4`
- Available for Settlement card: includes **`PrimaryButton "Settle Now" fullWidth mt-2`**

### Operator Symbols (between cards)
- Container: `size-4` (16×16), white bg, `rounded-[12px]`, `shrink-0`
- Minus: single `2px × 8px` bar, `bg-[#7e7e7e]`
- Plus: cross of `1.33px` bars
- Equals: two `1.33px × 8px` bars, `gap-[2px]`
- Order: Collections **−** Adjustments **−** Deductions **=** Settlement Processed **=** Available for Settlement

---

## 5. Chart Container Cards (Dashboard)

- Outer surface: `bg-[var(--surface-level-3,#fafafa)] p-8 rounded-tl-[32px] rounded-tr-[32px]`
- Chart block: `bg-white rounded-2xl p-[24px]` (16px radius via `rounded-2xl`)
- Payment Sources block: `bg-white rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-6`
- Legend rows (inside sources): `px-4 py-3 bg-[var(--surface-level-3,#fafafa)] rounded-lg`
- Actions widget: `bg-white rounded-2xl`; internal `p-[24px]` on tabs, `px-5 pb-5` on scroll area

