## 6. Feature / Service Cards (My Services, Connect Plus)

- Container: `bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-5 flex flex-col gap-4`
- Hover: `hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]`
- Grid: `grid grid-cols-2 gap-6`
- Icon: `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd] flex items-center justify-center`
- Title: `text-[14px] font-semibold text-[#101010]`
- Body: `text-[12px] text-[#7e7e7e] leading-[18px]`
- CTA: outline button `text-[12px] rounded-[8px] text-[#004299]` with `ArrowRight` `size-3.5`
- Status chip (when enabled): `px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[12px] font-semibold`
  - Enabled: `text-[#21c179] bg-[#e3f6ec]`

---

## 7. Device Cards (My Services)

- Container: `bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-5`
- Header: title left + "View All" hyperlink right (`text-[#004299] text-[12px]`)
- Grid: `grid grid-cols-2 gap-6`
- Sub-items: `bg-[#fafafa] hover:bg-accent/50 rounded-[8px] p-3 gap-3`
- Icon container: `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd] flex items-center justify-center`
- Device icons: inline SVGs (`CardMachineIcon`, `SoundBoxIcon`, `EMIIcon`, `AMCIcon`) — `currentColor` in tiles
- Status text: due = `text-[#ff9d00]`, paid = `text-[#21c179]`
- Navigation: `ChevronRight` `size-4`

---

## 8. Consent / Agreement Cards (Connect Plus)

- Container: `bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-6 flex flex-col gap-4`
- No hover effect
- Title: `text-[16px] font-semibold`
- Shield icon: `size-10 rounded-[12px] bg-[#00b8f5]` with `size-5 text-white ShieldCheck`
- Checkbox: `size-4 accent-[#004299]`, label `text-[14px]`, `items-center gap-3`
- Links in label: `text-[#00b8f5] font-semibold hover:underline`
- CTA: disabled state `bg-[#e0e0e0] text-[#7e7e7e] cursor-not-allowed`; enabled: custom Accept button

