## 9. Payment Acceptance Limit Card (Settings)

- Wrapper: `rounded-[12px] overflow-hidden`
- Main section: `bg-[#fafafa] p-6`
- Metrics in flex row with `w-px h-[40px] bg-[#e0e0e0]` vertical dividers
- Labels: `text-[14px] text-[#7e7e7e]`
- Values: `text-[16px] font-semibold text-[#101010]`
- Remaining value: `text-[#21c179]`
- CTA: `PrimaryButton "Upgrade Account"`
- Helper: `text-[12px] text-[#101010]`
- Footer: `h-px bg-[#e0e0e0]` divider + `px-6 py-3` warning `text-[12px] text-[#ff9d00]`

