## 10. Callout / Note Box (Reports)

- Container: `rounded-[8px] bg-[#fff4e0] px-4 py-3 max-w-[720px]`
- Title: `text-[14px] font-semibold text-[#101010]`
- Body: `text-[14px] text-[#7e7e7e]`
- No border, no hover, no CTA
- Warning-tinted (not error)

