## 12. Create Page Entry Cards (Payment Pages)

- Container: `border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-5`
- Hover: `hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]`
- Icon: `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd]`
- Title: `text-[14px] font-semibold`
- Body: `text-[12px] text-[#7e7e7e]`
