## Rules

### DO
- Use semantic token classes where available (`text-foreground`, `border-border`, `text-muted-foreground`)
- Maintain card-level `transition-colors` for hover states
- Use `flex-1` for equal-width summary cards in strip layouts
- Include divider (`border-t`) before card footers with links
- Wrap icon in background container for product/feature contexts

### DO NOT
- Apply hover to consent/agreement cards or callout boxes
- Use `font-semibold` in charges column (only on hyperlinks)
- Mix arbitrary hex without mapping to token table in `OVERVIEW.md`
- Use `bg-[#fafafa]` after `bg-[#F5F9FE]` in same className — last class wins
- Skip `shrink-0` on math operator symbols
